Sobha Developers Signs Loan to Build Homes in Gurgaon, India

-- B y   K a t r i n a   N i c h o l a s
-- 
2011-10-20T04:23:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-20/sobha-developers-signs-loan-to-build-homes-in-gurgaon-india.html
Sobha Developers Ltd. (SOBHA) , a housing
developer in India, signed a 4.725 billion rupee term loan due
October 2017, according to data compiled by Bloomberg.  Proceeds will be used to develop an integrated township in
the city of Gurgaon and Standard Chartered Plc and  Syndicate
Bank (SNDB)  provided the financing, the data show.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Katrina Nicholas at 
 knicholas2@bloomberg.net  